claim: Flublok contains 45 micrograms (mcg) of HA per strain vs 15 mcg of HA per strain in a standard-dose influenza vaccine.
explanation: Table listing contraindications and precautions for various 2022–23 influenza vaccines (egg-based IIVs and LAIV4, cell culture–based ccIIV4, recombinant RIV4) in persons with prior severe allergic reactions to different vaccine types. does not support the claim because the table contains information on allergic reaction contraindications and precautions, with no data on hemagglutinin microgram content per strain.
